variant_descriptions.KXORW: Bitwise XOR 16-bit masks k2 and k3 and place result in k1.
variant_descriptions.KXORB: Bitwise XOR 8-bit masks k2 and k3 and place result in k1.
variant_descriptions.KXORQ: Bitwise XOR 64-bit masks k2 and k3 and place result in k1.
variant_descriptions.KXORD: Bitwise XOR 32-bit masks k2 and k3 and place result in k1.

op.text: Performs a bitwise XOR between the vector mask k2 and the vector mask k3, and writes the result into vector mask k1 (three-operand form).
